article_title: $700K grant funding Valley health center expansion

article_metadata.news_keywords: , valley professionals community health center, terry j. warren
article_metadata.author: Nick Hedrick Tribune-Star

og.description: A Wabash Valley-based health care center is expanding beyond the immediate area, thanks to a $704,167 federal grant aimed at increasing medical access to communities in need.
